{"tid":465922,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"冬天去哈爾濱嗰頭既穿著問題","createTime":"2017-11-12T05:30:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-17T05:31:42.000Z","uid":51200,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"4149c516302745b6866822757ead22a89ffdcffa","tid":465922,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T05:30:58.000Z","msg":"小弟成十幾年無去過大陸，<br />\n淨係小學既時候去過上海。<br />\n因此，今個聖誕專登去中國睇下冰雕<br />\n<br />\n首先，想問下各位巴絲打，<br />\n哈爾濱/長春啲地容唔容許拖行李喼？定抑或我咩背囊會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其次，中國東北天氣應該好凍<br />\n小弟未去過天氣咁凍嘅地方，<br />\n之前係外國睇書，都係求其着件羽絨加長褲同普通鞋就已經OK<br />\n如果我去中國東北嘅話，有冇咩特別注意嘅衣着<br />\n又或者有冇一啲係巴絲打都推介嘅衣着<br />\n（例如，鞋/衫/褲/帽之類）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb6c0b1b4889d0cdbc827ee0e3bf2ea82967a437","tid":465922,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T05:36:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小弟成十幾年無去過大陸，<br />\n淨係小學既時候去過上海。<br />\n因此，今個聖誕專登去中國睇下冰雕<br />\n<br />\n首先，想問下各位巴絲打，<br />\n哈爾濱/長春啲地容唔容許拖行李喼？定抑或我咩背囊會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其次，中國東北天氣應該好凍<br />\n小弟未去過天氣咁凍嘅地方，<br />\n之前係外國睇<span style=\"color: red;\">雪</span>，都係求其着件羽絨加長褲同普通鞋就已經OK<br />\n如果我去中國東北嘅話，有冇咩特別注意嘅衣着<br />\n又或者有冇一啲係巴絲打都推介嘅衣着<br />\n（例如，鞋/衫/褲/帽之類）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ade18613569c0006fd5a7cd184ebc56be740cde3","tid":465922,"uid":113483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T05:42:06.000Z","msg":"我個陣拎20吋gip去<br />\n哈爾濱市內無太問題<br />\n去雪鄉個陣join 團<br />\n個行李可以放車"},{"pid":"e12a1b506592f4dd6c09fd45f9d4ce78aa7fb11f","tid":465922,"uid":113483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T05:45:24.000Z","msg":"其實衣物可以係當地買<br />\n對鞋最好boot款<br />\n面防水<br />\n<br />\n我個陣<br />\nHeat tech 內衣<br />\n冷衫<br />\n面衫 羽絨<br />\nHeat 褲同面褲<br />\n同兩對襪<br />\n著左對ugg 唔撚防水"},{"pid":"bf51fa9342afe99d77ebfff55b9a545223a175c1","tid":465922,"uid":124283,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T05:55:39.000Z","msg":"唔想下下著防水鞋可以買對防水襪旁身, 防水手襪都可以諗諗有無用既"},{"pid":"ee03a23df14e75c930ba8d3492716498852774bc","tid":465922,"uid":133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T08:13:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實衣物可以係當地買<br />\n對鞋最好boot款<br />\n面防水<br />\n<br />\n我個陣<br />\nHeat tech 內衣<br />\n冷衫<br />\n面衫 羽絨<br />\nHeat 褲同面褲<br />\n同兩對襪<br />\n著左對ugg 唔撚防水</blockquote><br />\nUGG <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2204ba9fb3ade905e5baa0c9d69673140b20f91","tid":465922,"uid":55542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T08:29:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"022103d8e395ece9cca40d90b9ff413dffdaa832","tid":465922,"uid":119494,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T08:39:20.0